          "content": "Of course. I am making that call now to the nearest Emergency Department to let them know you are coming. They will be waiting for you.\n\nI will also add a formal note to your chart that you specifically requested a CT head for your symptoms, so the team there is fully informed.\n\nPlease take all your previous medical records with you, especially anything from Dr. Sharma, if you have them. That can be very helpful.\n\nI will be here when you get back. Safe travels."
