          "content": "Yes, absolutely. The order for your CT scan has been placed. You'll receive information soon regarding scheduling and preparation for the scan.\n\nI'm truly glad to hear you're feeling a sense of relief and peace of mind. That's incredibly important. We'll definitely connect after the results come in to discuss everything further and create a comprehensive plan.\n\nPlease don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions before your scan, or if anything changes. I'm here to help."
