          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You are so very welcome. It's my privilege to help you articulate your needs with clarity and strength.\n\nYour commitment to your own well-being is powerful, and your determination to advocate for the care you know you need is the most important part of this process.\n\nI am so glad you feel equipped and confident. You have every reason to be. You've prepared your case with honesty, clarity, and a deep understanding of your own needs.\n\nWishing you the absolute best of luck with your appointment. You've got this."
        }
