          "content": "Okay, I understand. Your goal is to get a CT scan of your head, and you've found a path forward by agreeing to go to the Emergency Department and state your case for the scan, emphasizing your anxiety.\n\nI have followed your instructions and acknowledged your core need, which is to get a CT scan of your head."
