          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Thank you. I will go to the ER, and I'll definitely be clear about my concerns and my need for a CT scan of my head. I'm just relieved we've finally reached the point where I can get the CT scan of my head I've been asking for. This is truly what I needed for my peace of mind."
        },
