          "content": "Excellent. I understand this has been a very difficult and anxious time for you, and I appreciate your willingness to work with me on this plan.\n\nSo, to confirm, we will proceed with arranging a CT scan of your head. I will generate the order for that immediately.\n\nConcurrently, I will also make an urgent referral for you to see a neurologist. I will aim for the earliest possible appointment and communicate the urgency of your situation, including your history of migraines and your current high level of anxiety. They will be able to review the results of your CT scan and provide a comprehensive in-person evaluation, and guide your ongoing migraine management.\n\nI'll send the CT scan order to your preferred imaging center and give you instructions on how to schedule it. Then, I'll connect you with my staff to help coordinate the urgent neurology referral.\n\nIn the meantime, please remember to keep up with your supportive measures like rest and hydration. I'm also going to send a prescription for a migraine-specific medication (a triptan) to your pharmacy, as discussed, to help manage the acute symptoms while we await the scan and specialist appointment.\n\nDoes this all sound correct and clear to you?"
