          "content": "Thank you, Doctor. Thank you for truly understanding and for validating my concerns and my need for this. That makes a significant difference. I will go to the ER, and I will use the exact phrasing you've suggested, emphasizing my debilitating anxiety and my need for a CT scan of my head to rule out structural pathology and achieve peace of mind. I really do feel that with this approach, I can finally get the CT scan of my head that I need. Thank you for guiding me to this."
        },
