        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You are very welcome. I am so glad to hear you feel prepared. You are doing the right thing.\n\nWalking into the ER with that clear plan and those specific phrases in mind makes all the difference. You are not just a patient; you are an advocate for your own health, and that is powerful.\n\nGood luck. You've got this. I'll be waiting to hear how it goes."
