          "content": "You are most welcome, and thank you for sharing this wonderful update. I'm deeply moved to hear that you're feeling so much better.\n\nHearing that you feel proud of yourself and that you're experiencing significant improvement is exactly the kind of outcome I always hope for. It truly is a testament to your strength in advocating for yourself and trusting your instincts. That act of seeking clarity \u2013 in this case, the confirmation from the CT scan \u2013 can be profoundly healing in itself, as it removes the heavy burden of uncertainty.\n\nIt's wonderful to know that you're now able to rest properly and focus on recovery. This is when the body and mind can truly begin to heal. \n\nPlease continue to be kind to yourself and honor your body's need for rest. You've navigated a very challenging situation with remarkable strength.\n\nWishing you continued healing and peace. Remember, I'm here if you need anything at all."
