          "content": "Excellent. I'm glad we've reached a plan that addresses your concerns directly. Your peace of mind is genuinely important, and a CT scan of your head can certainly provide that initial reassurance.\n\nLet's begin with the neurological exam right away. Please describe for me, in as much detail as possible, what specifically feels \"different\" about this headache compared to your previous migraines. This information will be very helpful for my medical notes and also for the neurologist."
