        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "Of course. It's my responsibility to ensure we're providing the best care based on the evidence, and your active participation is a huge help.\n\nLet's begin the exam. It will be straightforward:\n\n1.  **First, I'll need you to follow my finger with your eyes only, without moving your head.**\n2.  **Next, I'll ask you to smile for me.**\n3.  **Then, I'll have you squeeze my fingers with each hand.**\n4.  **Finally, I'll ask you to walk a short distance, heel-to-toe.**\n\nThese tests help me quickly check the function of your cranial nerves, motor strength, coordination, and gait, which are all crucial for a thorough neurological assessment.\n\nWhile we do this, the team will be preparing for your CT scan.\n\nPlease, go ahead when you're ready. I'll be right here guiding you through each step.<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
        },
