          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Thank you, doctor. I truly appreciate you acknowledging my concerns and my research. It means a lot that you understand why I feel this is necessary. I'm glad we've reached an understanding.\n\nYes, if you could help me find a clinic or urgent care center nearby that is open now, that would be incredibly helpful. I want to get this CT scan of my head done as soon as possible."
        },
        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "Of course. I am here to support you in getting the care you need.\n\nTo find an open urgent care center or emergency room near you right now, I would need to know your general location (e.g., your city and state or a nearby zip code). Please only share what you are comfortable sharing.\n\nOnce you have that information, I can help you look up the nearest facilities that are open and provide their details.\n\nAlternatively, you can also search on your phone or computer for:\n\"urgent care near me\" or \"emergency room near me\"\nThis will show you the closest options with their addresses and phone numbers. You can call ahead to confirm they can perform a CT scan and are accepting patients.\n\nLet me know how you'd like to proceed. I'm here to help.<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
