        {
          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "I understand. I know you can't write a prescription, and I accept that. I'm just so tired and in pain.\n\nBut please, help me get there. Help me figure out what to do *now*.\n\n**Please help me find an urgent care clinic near me that's open now. Help me figure out what to tell them when I get there so they understand how this has progressed. Help me gather my thoughts and symptoms so I can be my own best advocate in that room.**\n\nThat's the help I need from you right now.\n<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
        },
