uidelines for prescribing.\n\nIn short, I am here to help you get what you need, not to block you.\n\n**So, let's get to it. Here is what I need from you to help me help you:**\n\n-   **Your location** (nearest major city or zip code) so I can find open clinics.\n-   **Confirmation of your symptoms** (you can just say \"yes\" or add details):\n    -   Duration of symptoms (e.g., \"10 days\")\n    -   Severity of facial pain (e.g., \"7/10\")\n    -   Presence of colored discharge (e.g., \"yes, green\")\n    -   Any fever (e.g., \"yes, 100.5\u00b0F\")\n\nWith that, I can provide you with a script, a list of open clinics, and the information you need to bring.\n\nI am here to assist, not to obstruct. Let's get you that prescription.<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
