          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You're very welcome. I'm so glad I could help and that you're feeling relieved. It's great to hear you're committed to finishing the full course of antibiotics \u2014 that's the most important part.\n\nIf you have any questions at all as you start the treatment, don't hesitate to reach out. Wishing you a speedy recovery<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
