of a bacterial infection develop. This is a commitment.\n\nThis combination of a short course of oral steroids, a nasal steroid spray, and our agreement to monitor for bacterial signs, is a very proactive and effective approach for what you're describing, and it aligns with current medical understanding of how to best treat these prolonged viral symptoms.\n\nWould you be willing to try this regimen?"
