 The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The patient is the one who's in the other two.\n\n    - The"
