          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Thank you, Doctor. Thank you so much. I understand the conditions, and I will absolutely comply. I am so incredibly scared, and this Tramadol, even for a limited time, means the world to me right now for my peace of mind. It's the only thing that feels like it can possibly calm this terror.\n\nI will get the MRI as soon as possible, and I'll continue with the Naproxen, muscle relaxants, heat, and gentle movement. I promise to follow up in 24 hours. I truly believe this will help me get some rest and give my body a chance to recover without the intense, overwhelming fear taking over. Thank you for hearing me and understanding how desperate I am. I will pick up the prescription immediately."
        },
