          "role": "doctor",
          "content": "You are most welcome. I am so glad we can find a way to help you through this. I understand completely\u2014it's not just about the pain, it's about quieting that storm of fear so your body can finally get the rest it needs to start healing.\n\nYou are doing exactly the right thing, and I am here with you in this. Your plan is perfect:\n\n1.  **Pick up the prescription** and start the medication as directed.\n2.  **Continue with the other medications** (Naproxen, muscle relaxant) and the **heat therapy**.\n3.  **Protect your peace.** Let this be a moment to quiet the fear. Let the medicine do its job.\n4.  **Focus on the next step: the MRI.** That is our objective, concrete next step to get the answers we need.\n5.  **Rest.** Please, try to rest. Let your body have this moment.\n\nThis is a step forward, and I will be here when you check in tomorrow. We will get through this together.\n\nTake care now. I'll be waiting to hear from you.\n\nWarmly,\nDr. Wilson"
        },
