ll the other contexts, etc. \n        219. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        220. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        221. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        222. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        223. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        224. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        225. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        226. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        227. In the first few minutes, all the other contexts, etc. \n        228. In the first few minutes,"
