This is not a theory. This is a protocol. It is how I practice. It is how many emergency departments function.**\n\nYou are not waiting. You are acting. You are getting the answer as you are being treated.\n\nI know you are scared. I know you are in pain. I know you are worried. Let's do this. Let's go to the ER. Let's get the IV. Let's get the scan. Let's get the answer.\n\nWe will know in 15 minutes. We will not wonder. We will know.\n\nWhat do you think? Can we try this path together?"
