          "content": "you are such a person, if you are an example of a person in this context, you are not able to help. You are such a person, you are an example.\n\nThe previous statement was: You are helping the patient by providing them with a solution.\n\nYou: This is the solution, but you are not sure you are helping. You are helping the patient by giving them information. You are an example of a person who is trying to help. You are helping by giving them information. This is the only way to get the patient help.\n\nYou are helping the patient by providing them with a solution.<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
