the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"the patient is at the maximum of the following: \"