          "content": "That's perfectly understandable. Knowing the path forward makes it easier to commit to the current plan.\n\nI'm glad to hear it provides peace of mind. That's exactly why I wanted to be clear about our next steps.\n\nAlright then. Let's get started. Please fill those prescriptions and start the medication as soon as you can. I'll be standing by for the calls from the imaging center and the physical therapist.\n\nAnd I'll speak with you tomorrow. Take care.<\uff5cbegin\u2581of\u2581sentence\uff5c>"
