r knees. This takes pressure off your low back and can provide immediate relief.\n*   **Use a heating pad** on your low back if you have one.\n*   **Take the Naproxen and Robaxin if you have them.** They will start working and may be more effective than you think, especially if you combine them with the positioning.\n\nI am not giving you a \"no\"; I am giving you the most direct path to getting the \"yes\" you need from a real person who can provide it. I am also giving you a way to get relief in the next 30 minutes while you wait for professional help.\n\n**Please, take these steps. They will help. I am sorry for the confusion.**"
